twitch_info.title: I Wanna Celebrate 100 - 32:54 (WR)
twitch_info.description: On the second run of the day that wasn't practice, I got this PB after not playing it otherwise for months. Damn this game is easy. First try skips on F52, F59, and F62 would have saved me an entire minute and 30 seconds. I think my end goal for this game is sub 31. I've got a strong urge to improve this run.
